  "content": "\n \n \n  <article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"4jKqmVg33goLOw19\">\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-bottom: 3px;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding: 5px 18px;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">01</span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;padding-left: 18px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>引言</strong></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-bottom: 0px;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">为文生图模型增加额外的控制条件一直是AIGC社区研究的重点之一，如ControlNet, IP-Adapter等一直是热门可控生成方法。近期，</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align: justify;\">魔搭社区联合浙江大学</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">对实体级可控文生图进行了探索，并开发了EliGen模型。</span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">EliGen可以对想要生成的图像中的每个实体的位置和细节进行控制，从而生成具有复杂场景和构图的图像。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"136445\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n       <table>\n        <tbody>\n         <tr>\n          <td valign=\"middle\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"word-break: break-all;background-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;\">手持化妆镜的美丽小姐姐</span><strong><strong style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\"></strong></strong><br></td>\n         </tr>\n         <tr>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016860\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4fe1e6b-f2c4-4db6-ac65-8d3fccd9ad00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing:0.578px;width:214px;font-size:15px;height:214px;text-align:left;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f4fe1e6b-f2c4-4db6-ac65-8d3fccd9ad00/public\"><span style=\"display: none;line-height: 0px;\">‍</span></td>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"457\" data-backw=\"457\" data-imgfileid=\"100016861\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/46a2bdb0-2269-49fd-24d8-e456a03d5c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"color:rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing:0.578px;width:223px;font-size:15px;height:223px;text-align:left;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/46a2bdb0-2269-49fd-24d8-e456a03d5c00/public\"></td>\n         </tr>\n        </tbody>\n       </table>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">EliGen提出了Regional Attention的注意力机制，对扩散模型中的Attention模块进行了通用扩展。同时，基于FLUX和Qwen2-VL，团队构建了500k样本的含有实体级标注的数据集，采用LoRA对EliGen进行了训练。EliGen不仅可以完成实体级的可控文生图任务，还可以对已有图像进行实体级局部重绘。同时，EliGen与社区模型：IP-Adapter、In-Context LoRA等结合，还可以应用在给定风格和角色的实体控制、Logo迁移等场景，具有无限可能。</span></p>\n   <section>\n    <iframe class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_3847626876940484610\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F8ZLuyaibrZbn5Pmv8icykEFUF2AeTgY1rvwuEOJ86iaF3YIgkKtHfxB3kvicicDAfq6icfxdF6ZZsSWGq8rvCYKVbx9g%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-w=\"1024\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_3847626876940484610\"></iframe>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">论文链接：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.01097</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">代码链接：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://github.com/modelscope/DiffSynth-Studio/tree/main/examples/EntityControl</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><br></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型链接：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://www.modelscope.cn/models/DiffSynth-Studio/Eligen</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n  </article>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-align: left;margin: 0px;text-indent: 0em;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\">在线Demo:</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"line-height: 1.6em;text-align: left;margin: 0px;text-indent: 0em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-decoration: none solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);\">https://www.modelscope.cn/studios/DiffSynth-Studio/EliGen</span>\n  </section>\n  <article data-identifier-application__slash__x-doc-key=\"4jKqmVg33goLOw19\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">02</span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>EliGen技术方案</strong></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong>Regional Attention实现</strong></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">EliGen提出了Regional Attention的机制，对扩散模型的注意力机制进行了扩展，使其支持基于任意形状空间信息的实体级控制。我们采用结构化文本向量来表示条件控制信息，包括描述图像整体内容的全局提示词（global prompt）和描述具体细节的多个局部提示词（local prompts）。每个local prompt都附带一个掩码（mask），用于表示其生成区域。基于这些mask，我们针对实体内、实体间和实体与图像的关系构建了attention mask，保证了每个实体的token序列只作用于特定区域。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"344\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100016834\" data-ratio=\"0.5953703703703703\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0586b555-60d7-4458-c42c-fbfb495bcc00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0586b555-60d7-4458-c42c-fbfb495bcc00/public\"></p>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\">训练数据生成和模型训练</span></strong></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">使用Regional Attention对模型进行扩展后，可以发现它不经过训练也能改变某些区域的实体属性，比如颜色。但是未经训练的模型无法控制图像的布局。为了激活EliGen的空间控制能力，我们构建了带实体标注的数据集，采用LoRA，对实体控制任务进行了特化训练。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如下图所示，我们从DiffusionDB数据集的文本Prompt出发，使用FLUX.1-dev生成了500k训练图像。进一步，利用Qwen2-VL 72B的强大图像理解和grounding能力，对训练样本进行了重描述 (recaption)，同时对图像中的实体的语义和位置信息进行了标注。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"345\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"100016832\" data-ratio=\"0.5972222222222222\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f79f7a4-475d-4972-eb2b-0e40e840e700/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8f79f7a4-475d-4972-eb2b-0e40e840e700/public\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最终，经过训练，EliGen模型具有出色的实体级位置和细节控制能力，图像生成质量远超同类模型，在许多场景都有应用的潜力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><br></span></p>\n   <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;margin:10px auto;outline:0px;visibility:visible;display:flex;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;justify-content:center;\">\n    <section style=\"padding-bottom: 3px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: skew(-10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n     <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;visibility:visible;\">\n      <section style=\"padding: 5px 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;display: flex;align-items: center;transform: skew(10deg);visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;transform-style: preserve-3d;visibility: visible;\">\n        <section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);transform: translateZ(10px);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n         <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\">03</span>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"padding-left: 18px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;color: rgb(6, 84, 234);text-align: left;visibility: visible;\">\n        <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>应用场景</strong></span>\n       </section>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;font-size: 18px;font-weight: bolder;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></span></p>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;outline: 0px;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><br></p>\n   <h2 style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 17px;color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\"><strong>复杂构图的实体级构建</strong></span></h2>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">代码：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">https://github.com/modelscope/DiffSynth-Studio/blob/main/examples/EntityControl/entity_control.py</span></p>\n   <p><br></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"136445\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n       <table>\n        <tbody>\n         <tr>\n          <td valign=\"middle\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"word-break: break-all;background-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;\">月下的海天一色</span><strong style=\"color:rgb(0, 82, 255);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;text-align:left;\"></strong></td>\n         </tr>\n         <tr>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016864\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7d293dc-56e2-4457-0bad-7abfb1797b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"height: 412px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 412px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c7d293dc-56e2-4457-0bad-7abfb1797b00/public\"></td>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016865\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f2b413a-02e6-4b5a-0ce7-ed4ea4a1be00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"height: 412px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 412px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6f2b413a-02e6-4b5a-0ce7-ed4ea4a1be00/public\"></td>\n         </tr>\n        </tbody>\n       </table>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p><br></p>\n   <p><br></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"136445\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n       <table>\n        <tbody>\n         <tr>\n          <td valign=\"middle\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"word-break: break-all;background-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;\">太阳初升的朝圣</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 15px;text-align: left;\"></strong></td>\n         </tr>\n         <tr>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016868\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60e8a069-f2e5-4de6-c5d1-0a78fb0f3500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"height: 412px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 412px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/60e8a069-f2e5-4de6-c5d1-0a78fb0f3500/public\"></td>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016870\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62cde85f-7c00-4185-22c8-a4196cab5400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"height: 412px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 412px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/62cde85f-7c00-4185-22c8-a4196cab5400/public\"></td>\n         </tr>\n        </tbody>\n       </table>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n   <p><br></p>\n   <p><br></p>\n   <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"136445\">\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      <section data-autoskip=\"1\">\n       <table>\n        <tbody>\n         <tr>\n          <td valign=\"middle\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"word-break: break-all;background-color: rgb(0, 82, 255);\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;\">为EliGen举牌打call</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 255);font-size: 15px;text-align: left;\"></strong></td>\n         </tr>\n         <tr>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016873\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c1ee23c-9e4c-434e-cc03-2da4c57c8b00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"height: 412px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-align: left;width: 412px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c1ee23c-9e4c-434e-cc03-2da4c57c8b00/public\"></td>\n          <td width=\"244\" valign=\"top\" style=\"word-break: break-all;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100016874\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://ima